item.description: Template + Prompt Prompt~01 Subject: A woman in her early twenties with short, fluffy, and ruffled hairs. She is an endowed and athletic woman. She is wearing a bright red bikini with red stilettos and a yellow scarf. A simple necklace with a diamond pendant resting just above her breasts. She is wearing hanging earrings. She has tattoos on her arms and thighs. She is smiling confidently with amusement. She is captured from head to toe.
